item.title: A Gfx Section
item.dc:creator: @reyx7 reyx7
item.description:
@reyx7 wrote:

Tribbinator:

Well seeing as this is Moparscape…The model section we have is for RSPS, therefore a GFX section would be for GFX for runescape private servers, and last time I checked we do not have many custom animators or interface creators (Interfaces created outside of Lin’s interface creator) I may be very wrong, as I dont travel out of the model section often but, Thats my view

Well maybe that’s what’s needed to get done. Plus, you could always have like, textures and stuff. Or concept art.
